Kiwix 0.9 beta5
* New supported user interface languages: cs, hsb, tt-cyrl, dsb, hi, gu
* Fixed the letton language menu item (ID: 3439113)
* Switch off automatically if loading random article
* Avoiding duplicates in publisher & language filters in the content manager (ID: 3439108)	
* In the library, pressing <ENTER> in your local library directly open the file
* Greying "Load random article" menu entry if no content is loaded (ID: 3439112)
* Add the support of the "publisher" ZIM Metadata
* Fix many localisation files which were broken due to a buggy script (ID: 3440627)
* Fix a wrong behaviour in case of two portable kiwix consecutive runs (ID: 3442083)
* Improve the library menus visibility (ID: 3439109)
* Fix different issues relative to ISO language codes (ID: 3439293)
* Improve code and documentation of kiwix-manage
* In library, add a option to keep ZIM file in case of content deletion (ID: 3442084)
* Add "Copy Link Address" in contextual menu for external links (ID: 3444066)
* Add a security to avoid "displaying" window outside the screen (ID: 3415334)

